items.title: Slate Auto drops ‘under $20,000’ pricing after Trump administration ends federal EV tax credit
items.description: Slate Auto has updated its website after Congress passed President Trump's tax cut bill, which will eliminate the federal EV tax credit.

items.title: Everyone in tech has an opinion about Soham Parekh
items.description: There is now a new badge of honor for startup founders: your proximity to one previously unknown Indian software engineer named Soham Parekh.

items.title: Cluely’s ARR doubled in a week to $7M, founder Roy Lee says. But rivals are coming.
items.description: Cluely's rapid ascend may be challenged by free copycat products.

items.title: Who is Soham Parekh, the serial moonlighter Silicon Valley startups can’t stop hiring?
items.description: Stories about Soham Parekh, a software engineer that simultaneously works at several startups, have gone viral in the last week. Who is he?

items.title: TechCrunch All Stage brings back early launch prices for a limited time
items.description: Ticket rates have officially rolled back with savings of up to $425, as TechCrunch All Stage becomes startup central July 15 in Boston.
